{"tid":1250270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［必聽神曲］一人掟磚會受傷","createTime":"2019-06-22T04:17:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T13:37:57.000Z","uid":265019,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1646d848e37e7b331e51274da1d20fb05e4df589","tid":1250270,"uid":265019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:17:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/134916363241461/posts/2384860554913686?s=1578001899&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F134916363241461%2Fposts%2F2384860554913686%3Fs%3D1578001899%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=Hh5C2Wm8JWR9usSbwEl%2Bh%2FjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=e48bfb36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/134916363241461/posts/2384860554913686?s=1578001899&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n何以你那天包抄中信 我會咁緊張<br />\n<br />\n誰令我 衝進大堂<br />\n<br />\n何以我跌低趴係地處 你卻照樣盅<br />\n<br />\n狂揼我 警官警長<br />\n<br />\n不知哪個方向 又傳來了開槍<br />\n<br />\n再次擊碎心中的理想<br />\n<br />\n一人掟磚會受傷 五人暴動啊太混帳<br />\n<br />\n差人對準左佢先發射 面部中槍<br />\n<br />\n商台記者紀念媽<br />\n<br />\n議員為割席惆悵<br />\n<br />\n警員老頂想卸走隻鑊 實在太吹脹"},{"pid":"8a3b82bd7895bc3284c2b95c7edd73b637596296","tid":1250270,"uid":265019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:23:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"669aaf8db59a6e90bf22545524b31bb86ccad4fe","tid":1250270,"uid":262125,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:23:50.000Z","msg":"推 我嗰時仲要食緊早餐笑到噴"},{"pid":"7ab17e371a33395cd0a4c713e1a71fd5b4b1e4cc","tid":1250270,"uid":265019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"669aaf8db59a6e90bf22545524b31bb86ccad4fe","tid":1250270,"uid":262125,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:23:50.000Z","msg":"推 我嗰時仲要食緊早餐笑到噴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime